<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Beazer Homes USA as buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Beazer Homes USA as buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said analyst Ivy Schneider initiated coverage of Beazer Homes USA Inc with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- estimated earnings of $2.17 per share for 1997, and $2.74 for 1998, versus $2.01 for 1996.</p>
<p>-- set price target of $16-$17 over next six months. Shares rose 5/8 to 14-3/4.</p>
</text>
